			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4004526">
									

<p>I'm a bit confused. Considering the Foundation is trusted by every single major government on the planet to deal with the anomalous, why would the FBI pull this off? The Foundation has been around for millennia considering SCP-2000, etc.</p>
<p>I understand the GOC, since the Foundation doesn't exactly like terminating bixbys, etc. and sometimes that shit needs to be done, but the FBI making their own Foundation seems strange</p>

