														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4115887">
									

<p>I believe that the FBI has a duty to protect the nation from anything and everything. Because of this, the federal government or leaders of the FBI may want to either (1) Keep their own records of SCP's because the Foundation is unknown to them or (2) to keep tabs on the Foundation as a sort of &quot;This is what the Foundation did today&quot; sort of thing.</p>
<p>It kind of reminds me of the X-Files. They investigated things that were already controlled by the government on some level. Sometimes they even investigated the government. Something similar to that is my best guess.</p>

